  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Comparison of HTC experiences</measure>
    <time_frame>10 months</time_frame>
    <description>Number of ANC clients who meet an expected result of a survey with the intervention group (IPV/GBV-HTC) or with the control group (standard HTC). The score is based on answers given to attitudes toward study participant knowledge regarding IPV/GBV; awareness of IPV/GBV services; and agency regarding talking with their partner about HIV testing.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
